 *Shadow Cat looked up as Iron Raptor came in, She saw
that iron was severly damaged but looked like she had
a good time. She smiled, Iron always did love battle.
She walked up to her and asked,*

 " Did you have a good time, Dear?"

 *She grinned and patted Iron on the shoulder. She
then became serious and asked.*

 " Have you seen Snow Tech? He is supposed to meet me
here so we can go get our stuff. Jeeze, guys are
always late, excpecially the doepy ones."

 *She gave Prowl a meaningful look, and went to help
the two bots to the Cr chambers*

-------------------------------------------------------

 * Snow Tech sighed. He was pooped. trying to get to
one place to another trying not be noticed was hard
work. He let out a devistating fart that wilted the
folige around him.*

 " Ooops!"

 * That was a bad thing to do, not only did he give
away his position, he smelled up his armour too.*

 " jeeze, better check for skid marks! That was a
doozey! Whoa and ranchy!!!"

 * He got up on wobbly legs and began to head for the
Ark, trying not to let anything suprise him, the
results could be devistating!!!*
